%% Diagram: Component Composition Primitives Map
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    Q{What are you<br/>composing?}

    Q -->|Same shape,<br/>different content| PROPS["Props + children<br/>e.g. Card title prop,<br/>Layout children"]
    Q -->|One parent,<br/>related children| COMPOUND["Compound components<br/>e.g. Tabs.List / Tabs.Panel,<br/>Menu.Item / Select.Option"]
    Q -->|Behaviour without UI| HEADLESS["Hooks / Headless<br/>e.g. useCombobox(),<br/>Dialog.Root / Trigger"]
    Q -->|Same behaviour,<br/>different rendering| RENDER["Render props /<br/>function-as-children<br/>e.g. virtualised list,<br/>FormField render={...}"]
    Q -->|Cross-cutting service<br/>or DI| CTX["Context provider<br/>e.g. SdkProvider,<br/>ThemeProvider"]
    Q -->|Wrap many components<br/>with the same chrome| HOC["Higher-order component<br/>legacy; prefer hooks<br/>e.g. withErrorBoundary"]

    classDef question fill:#3D3D3D,stroke:#1F1F1F,color:#fff
    classDef pattern fill:#2E5A88,stroke:#1F4870,color:#fff
    classDef legacy fill:#7A4A2D,stroke:#5A3520,color:#fff
    class Q question
    class PROPS,COMPOUND,HEADLESS,RENDER,CTX pattern
    class HOC legacy
